message.body: Hey dude! Been writing papers all week - handed in 47 pages! Just super busy with school right now. What ab you?

Wowza, congrats. Turned in a 5 pager this morning, 30 min presentation this evening, 3 finals next week and now i need to stop procrastinating on my spanish project. When is you madness done? Will you have any time to kick it this weekend?
